w to liquidate your company\">company liquidations</a> </li>\n  <li><a href=\"/options-for-paying-off-your-debts/debt-relief-orders\" title=\"Debt Relief Orders\">Debt Relief Orders (DRO)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/options-for-paying-off-your-debts/individual-voluntary-arrangements\" title=\"Individual Voluntary Arrangement (IVA)\">Individual Voluntary Arrangements (<abbr title=\"Individual Voluntary Arrangement\">IVA</abbr>)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/company-voluntary-arrangements\" title=\"Company Voluntary Arrangement (CVA)\">Company Voluntary Arrangements (<abbr title=\"Company Voluntary Arrangement\">CVA</abbr>)</a> </li>\n  <li><a href=\"/complain-about-a-limited-company\" title=\"Complain about a limited company\">reporting misconduct of trading companies</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Bankruptcy and insolvency are handled by the <a href=\"http://www.aib.gov.uk/about/contact-us\" title=\"Contact the Accountant in Bankruptcy\" rel=\"external\">Accountant in Bankruptcy</a> in Scotland, and the <a href=\"http://www.detini.gov.uk/insolvency-contacts.htm\" title=\"Contact the Northern Ireland Insolvency Service\" rel=\"external\">Northern Ireland Insolvency Service</a>  in Northern Ireland.</p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[{"title":"Court claims, debt and bankruptcy","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/tax%2Fcourt-claims-debt-bankruptcy.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes recovering debts, registering for bankruptcy and as a creditor","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=tax%2Fcourt-claims-debt-bankruptcy","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax/court-claims-debt-bankruptcy"},"parent":{"title":"Money and tax","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/tax.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes VAT, debt and inheritance tax","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/